{"tid":1044950,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被發現使用了盗版程序的(G)I-DLE 田小娟親自發文道歉「正在深切反省」","createTime":"2019-03-03T09:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T10:28:03.000Z","uid":152432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8c92f9311a8e247c1156f24a9513835d5184db","tid":1044950,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:15:40.000Z","msg":"小娟首先坦承過去曾使用並持有盜版軟體檔案，對此她正在深切地反省。「我記得那是在我剛開始學作曲時，曾經學著用過幾個作曲所需的程式。針對我沒有把以前的程式全部刪除整理乾淨，甚至沒意識到這件事情的部分，我也在深切地反省當中。」<br />\n<br />\n「雖然自從我正式開始作曲至今，所有相關軟體全都使用官方版本的，但無論在任何狀況中，我都應該更加留意創作者的著作權，並且該經過深思熟慮後才行動。我的無知讓大家擔心了，再次向大家致上歉意。」<br />\n<br />\n  小娟最後也承諾未來會更加認真瞭解後才行動，以便不再使用或持有任何非法軟體。<br />\n身為當前最被看好的新生代創作偶像之一，小娟坦承曾侵害他人著作權的勇氣也很值得肯定，相信經此一事她也會有更多成長的吧！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/171527_29c43a8d3d7f2f869dcd5118ae51e8ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F171527_29c43a8d3d7f2f869dcd5118ae51e8ae.jpg&h=10dce272&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/171531_6c8a100e3f69ffaffbcffbfe5d2f7482.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F171531_6c8a100e3f69ffaffbcffbfe5d2f7482.jpg&h=8d221b3b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18cdf7a3983c3b57ff98c2067c18968911a91297","tid":1044950,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/171838_b629eeef160894580ab41f698c9b24de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F171838_b629eeef160894580ab41f698c9b24de.jpg&h=0bb34ba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/171841_56155e0312726823fbee7b7805bc1297.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F171841_5615